# DVC Parameters Template
# 
# INSTRUCTIONS FOR DATA SCIENTISTS:
# 1. Copy this file to params.yaml in project root
# 2. Uncomment the section for your task (supervised/unsupervised)
# 3. Add your model's specific hyperparameters
# 4. Delete unused sections and these instructions
